Hi Selection Syndicate,

The latest round of evaluations is complete. Key takeaways:

• All candidates demonstrated strong technical fundamentals, with particularly strong performance in backend development and problem-solving.

• Each candidate’s detailed assessment, including interview notes and skill matrices, has been uploaded to the assessment workspace for your review.

• Recommendations for potential team alignment are included in the workspace.

Please let me know if you need additional insights or would like to schedule a debrief.

Best regards,
Jane
